== 司法人员 ==
初级裁判所包含法官和其他成员。符合法定条件的前裁判所成员在管辖权转移时都将成为初级裁判所法官，而非法律专业人士（通常是前裁判所专门领域之专家）作为其他成员继续存在。新的法官和成员由司法任命委员会任命。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tribunals.gov.uk/Tribunals/Upper/upper.htm#q2|title=Upper Tribunal: What has changed?|publisher=Tribunals Service|accessdate=10 November 2010|archive-date=2012-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121030150503/http://www.tribunals.gov.uk/tribunals/upper/upper.htm#q2|dead-url=no}}</ref>

此外，下列人士亦可作为初级審裁處法官出庭：<ref>Sections 4 and 6 of the [http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2007/15 Tribunals, Courts and Enforcement Act 2007] {{Wayback|url=http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2007/15 |date=20131127223227 }}, Legislation.gov.uk, Retrieved 10 November 2010</ref>

* 上级裁判所法官
* 上诉法院法官
* 苏格兰民事法庭法官
* 高级法院法官
* 巡回法院法官及治安法官
* 地区法官及地区裁判法院法官

初级裁判所由裁判庭高级主席主持，目前是Carnwath大法官。每个裁判庭均有庭长，分庭有首席法官。<ref>See [http://www.tribunals.gov.uk/Tribunals/Documents/President/StructureOfTheTS.pdf First-tier and Upper Tribunals Structure Chart] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tribunals.gov.uk/Tribunals/Documents/President/StructureOfTheTS.pdf |date=20101015082447 }} and, for example, the [http://www.tribunals.gov.uk/Tribunals/Documents/Grc/GRC_PJs_23jul10.pdf structure chart for the General Regulatory Chamber] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tribunals.gov.uk/Tribunals/Documents/Grc/GRC_PJs_23jul10.pdf |date=20120306095815 }}, Tribunals Service, Retrieved 10 November 2010</ref>

大多数案件当中，判决由一名法官与两名其他成员作出，但各庭及各分庭亦有不同，根据个案也有变化。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tribunals.gov.uk/tribunals/Rules/rules.htm#psspt|title=Practice Statements on Composition of Tribunals|publisher=Tribunals Service|accessdate=10 November 2010|archive-date=2012-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306095822/http://www.tribunals.gov.uk/tribunals/Rules/rules.htm#psspt|dead-url=no}}</ref>
== 上诉 ==
大多数案件可以上诉之上级裁判所，但需要的到初级裁判所或上级裁判所的许可。行使损害赔偿和政治庇护支持的案件一般无上诉权，但可以申请上级裁判所对初级裁判所的裁决进行审查。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tribunals.gov.uk/Tribunals/FAQ/faq.htm|title=Frequently Asked Questions - 2: Can I appeal against a decision made by the First–tier Tribunal?|publisher=Tribunals Service|accessdate=10 November 2010|archive-date=2012-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306095838/http://www.tribunals.gov.uk/Tribunals/FAQ/faq.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

